                  </hi>. I live in Elizabeth-terrace, Liverpool-road. I am not in business—this is my handkerchief—I knew nothing of its being taken till the officer told me.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. Have mercy on me; I did not take it. He found it a good way from me, and he says there were two girls with me—if there was, how could he see me?</p>
